@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam RoundCorner 18
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

rectangle "External LILA / Leech run" as Run
artifact "raw train log\nstep / train_loss / val_loss" as RawLog
component "35_lila_log_to_csv.py" as Adapter
artifact "aligned CSV\nstep, train_loss, val_loss" as Aligned
component "36_lila_training_dynamics.py" as Dyn
component "37_lila_delta_cone_analysis.py" as Cone
artifact "timing plot\nloss + derivative" as Plot
artifact "delta-cone rank\nforward / cone fractions" as ConeOut
artifact "Phase 2 comparison surface" as Surface

Run --> RawLog
RawLog --> Adapter
Adapter --> Aligned
Aligned --> Dyn
Aligned --> Cone
Dyn --> Plot
Cone --> ConeOut
Plot --> Surface
ConeOut --> Surface

note bottom of Surface
Empirical alignment first:
timing, spikes, derivative mass,
then optional SR/CN and sample audits.
end note
@enduml
